                                    friender_device_id, friender_licence_id,
                                    friendee_device_id, friendee_licence_id
                                ) VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4)

2c20127a37b1228fee57abf480e881fe14b91fa9.query:
INSERT INTO
                users(device_id, licence_id, mii, location, latitude, longitude)
            VALUES
                ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
            ON CONFLICT (device_id, licence_id) DO UPDATE SET
                mii = $3,
                location = $4,
                latitude = $5,
                longitude = $6
            RETURNING vs_rating, bt_rating
